%p Attractive semi-detached cottage with airy beamed sitting room and lovely country views. The well-equipped open plan kitchen has an electric cooker, fridge and microwave. The lounge area has a pine dining table and benches, and attractive soft furnishings. This leads to a lobby and loo and cute downstairs bathroom with a small step bath - popular with children and elderly people. The back door opens onto the utility room and studio. Cottage stairs lead up to a pretty dorma double bedroom with connecting twin beds and en-suite loo and shower room, and an adjoining small children's room with built in bunk beds.


