%p Converted semi-detached cottage with character features and exposed beams, backing onto the wooded hillside with stream. Entrance into comfortably furnished lounge from small walled courtyard. The open plan kitchen has an electric cooker, fridge and microwave. Cottage style wrought iron stairs lead to a dorma bedroom with connecting twin beds and ensuite shower room with adjoining small single bedroom. The light, airy rooms have views over the fields and into the valley woods and orchard.


